name: InhaledCorticosteroidsIC
title: Inhaled corticosteroids (IC)
purpose:
(Clinical Focus: Inhaled corticosteroids: Used to identify all inhalation medications that include corticosteroids.),(Data Element Scope: DRUG_CLASS_MEMBERS: PHARMACOLOGIC:),(Inclusion Criteria: Associated with the IN or PIN for 
Beclomethasone Dipropionate (PIN =1348),
Budesonide (IN =19831),
Ciclesonide (IN = 274964),
Fluticasone Furoate (PIN =705022),
Fluticasone Propionate (PIN = 50121).
Mometasone (IN =108118),
Mometasone Furoate (PIN =30145)
Includes combinations drugs that include these ingredients.),(Exclusion Criteria: (1) TTY in {DF, DFG}. (2) Specifies route other than inhaled.)
